title: Putin is almost sure of victory, but what's next?
text:
Putin is almost sure of victory, but what's next? 4:08am EDT - 01:51 
As soon as the party is over on Sunday night to celebrate Vladimir Putin's re-election, the Russian leader will confront a nasty hangover: he has no plan for what to do once his time in office runs out.
